reviewText: Rip off!!  The DVD won't play on an American DVD player, so I can't watch them.

Don't bother with this if you are looking for the Digital Ultraviolet download to work! This one's going back since the price paid was to include the Digital download.
glad to get the series as I believe this has been the best thing ever
